{"tid":957761,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"屯門新盤珀御開放式 月租僅9千","createTime":"2018-12-27T09:27:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-29T05:50:36.000Z","uid":19552,"like":6,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"21e8fb5a48a651213374805baa1e3a3ba237055b","tid":957761,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T09:27:33.000Z","msg":"屯門租金多月以來回落，更蔓延至入伙新盤市場，其中珀御一個新入伙單位月租僅9,000元，屬近期新低。<br />\n<br />\n屯門近日租金回落，不少租賃成交價跌穿1萬元，情況更蔓延至入伙新盤。珀御本月至今錄約10宗成交，當中有2宗月租為1萬元以下。一個中層E室單位，面積296平方呎，屬開放式設計，月租僅9,000元，呎租約30元，屬屋苑新低租金。業主於2017年以約437萬元購入單位，現時租金回報約2.4厘。<br />\n<br />\n二手市場樓價下跌，令不少區內業主轉賣為租，因而令租盤急增，租金受壓更錄下跌趨勢。本月屯門區內錄約177宗租賃，便有約44宗為萬元以下的租賃成交，佔約25%。"},{"pid":"e8fcba61c57f37049db5c539d2b59bfba50cbaff","tid":957761,"uid":78791,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T09:28:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bdfc5f319c0e01d0085e57661270970205368125","tid":957761,"uid":19552,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T09:33:03.000Z","msg":"AA一定水鳩人放租50蚊一呎"},{"pid":"fb6148c03ed5aa19112a91b5df1cfd330dec8754","tid":957761,"uid":37733,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T09:35:24.000Z","msg":"係盈豐隔離 好多野食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fae25e48906e4c573f9baa2c6bf8fb317e9c7079","tid":957761,"uid":88029,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T09:39:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7bca6c9b077fcb01106bea006116c1ee38300782","tid":957761,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T09:45:25.000Z","msg":"港紙定期都屌打左租金回報"},{"pid":"cbb3dd6eb7cbd3cab70adeec1c74dfb8c3fff767","tid":957761,"uid":42921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T09:51:14.000Z","msg":"2.4厘<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/face